list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment: Eclipse config and class diagram for monitor.implementation.session. Also fix some concurrency bugs in session pool.

task.summary:
Improve the loading of configuration data.
Look for config.properties in the location specified by the DataDirectory system property. If this fails, look in the classpath for config.properties.
Fix session management tests by removing stale data in the session pool after closing all sessions. This is only needed for tests. It isn't necessary when shutting down.
Eclipse config and class diagram for monitor.implementation.session. Also fix some concurrency bugs in session pool.

Stop SessionClosingRunnable asking ProcessKiller to kill the sub-processes in the Session it created to kill the subprocesses in another session. This frees ProcessKiller from the endless task of creating processes which which it then tries to kill.
